I"<h1 id="6w-method">6W Method</h1>

<p>Have you ever found yourself in a situation where you’re not sure what to do next? Maybe you’re feeling overwhelmed by a project, or you’ve hit a roadblock in your work. The 6W Method can help you figure out what to do next.</p>

<p>The 6W Method is a simple framework that you can use to analyze a problem and come up with a plan of action. It’s called the 6W Method because it involves answering six questions:</p>

<ol>
  <li>What is the problem?</li>
  <li>Who is affected by the problem?</li>
  <li>What are the potential causes of the problem?</li>
  <li>What are the possible solutions to the problem?</li>
  <li>What are the risks and benefits of each solution?</li>
  <li>What is the best way to implement the chosen solution?</li>
</ol>

<p>Making a 6W Method is a simple way to figure out what to do next. It’s a helpful tool to use when you’re feeling overwhelmed or stuck. By answering these six questions, you can develop a plan of action and move forward.</p>
